<p>here's the concept of my program. there is a combobox that has year (from 1915-present) and textBox that will display the Age.</p>  <p>here's my idea</p>  <pre><code>Dim today as integer'this is where i want to store the current year     Dim year as integer'stores selected items from combobox Dim age as Integer       year = combobox.selectedItem age = year - today  txtbox.text = age 'displays age on textbox </code></pre>